HEADWORD: Cooncan
<hw>Coon"can</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Corrupt of
<ets>conquian</ets>.]</ety> <def>A game of cards derived from conquian,
played by two or more players with one or two full packs of
cards.</def>⟦br⟧
